text: Zella-Mehlis is a town in the Schmalkalden Meinigen district, in Thuringia, Germany. It is in the Thuringian Forest, north of Suhl, and east of Meiningen. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Verwaltungsgemeinschaftfrei towns in Thuringia Category:Schmalkalden-Meiningen Rural District
title: Zella-Mehlis
